11.688-1.264c1.248-1.244 1.258-7.4 1.258-7.4 0-.035-.014-6.157-1.258-7.398zm-16.656 3.608H9.268v8.894H7.566v-8.894H5.807v-1.512h5.22v1.512zM16 28.439h-1.507v-.843c-.281.312-.569.55-.873.711a1.816 1.816 0 0 1-.877.244c-.35 0-.61-.112-.79-.343-.174-.23-.264-.569-.264-1.028v-6.419h1.508v5.889c0 .183.032.313.093.395.067.082.17.122.31.122.111 0 .253-.054.422-.163.17-.108.324-.245.469-.411V20.76H16v7.679zm5.478-1.585c0 .543-.118.959-.355 1.25-.234.291-.579.433-1.027.433-.297 0-.559-.054-.789-.166a1.937 1.937 0 0 .405.049.685.147.842.102.157.271.233.512.233.25 0 .425-.066.524-.198.099-.132.151-.423.151-.876v-.35h1.552v.394c0 .788-.188 1.38-.568 1.781-.376.397-.942.594-1.693.594-.675 0-1.209-.209-1.597-.632-.387-.42-.585-1.001-.585-1.742V22.83c0-.664.215-1.209.642-1.628.426-.419.976-.629 1.653-.629.691 0 1.222.195 1.594.583.371.387.555.945.555 1.674v1.958z"></path><path d="M24.499 0-.32.074c-.105.05-.208.129-.311.234v4.784c.122.123.242.217.359.271a.85.85 0 0 0 .364.083c.185 0 .32-.054.407-.163.086-.107.132-.281.132-.528v-3.965c0-.259-.054-.457-.16-.59-.11-.134-.268-.2-.471-.2zm5.199-10.425h-1.7v-.934c-.31.343-.637.608-.977.786-.339.18-.667.27-.986.27-.396 0-.689-.126-.888-.378-.198-.252-.298-.629-.298-1.134V3.006h1.697V9.49c0 .2.039.345.11.434.069.09.187.135.345.135.124 0 .283-.06.474-.178.19-.118.366-.27.523-.456V3.006h1.7v8.458zm-6.901-8.056c-.451-.41-1.028-.615-1.731-.615-.771 0-1.387.195-1.844.583-.459.387-.688.909-.687 1.565v4.383c0 .719.224 1.29.668 1.716.447.424 0-.399-.062-.519-.189-.12-.129-.182-.307-.182-.538V4.877c0-.185.067-.335.195-.449a.745.745 0 0 1 .507-.17c.223 0 .405.056.543.17a.553.553 0 0 1 .208.449v4.607zM8.702 0H6.774l2.279 3.86v281.825s-58.34-39.336-144.78-39.336C185.868 246.35 39.334 258.087 0 66.843c0 0 26.438 23.272 81.073 23.272 88.234 0 116.866-86.257 319.112-86.257" fill="#fccb06"></path></symbol></svg></div>

<div id="wrap">
  
  <div id="translations" role="navigation" class="show">
   <div class="links">
    <div class="welcome">Welcome, football fans from around the world!</div>
    <div><span class="use">Use FBref in: </span>
    <div class="langs">
                       <a class="pt" onclick="sr_set_trans_choice('pt');" href="https://fbref.com/pt/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats">Português</a>
         ·                        <a class="en" onclick="sr_set_trans_choice('en');" href="https://fbref.com/en/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats">English</a>
         ·                        <a class="fr" onclick="sr_set_trans_choice('fr');" href="https://fbref.com/fr/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats">Français</a>
         ·                        <a class="it" onclick="sr_set_trans_choice('it');" href="https://fbref.com/it/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats">Italiano</a>
         ·                        <a class="de" onclick="sr_set_trans_choice('de');" href="https://fbref.com/de/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats">Deutsch</a>
         ·                        <a class="es" onclick="sr_set_trans_choice('es');" href="https://fbref.com/es/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats">Español</a>
                    </div>
    </div>
  </div>
<div class="closer" onclick="sr_set_trans_choice('en',true, true)"></div>
</div>

<script>



var sr_lang_curr   = 'en';
var sr_lang_cookie = 'sr_lang';
var sr_lang_confirmed_cookie = 'sr_lang_confirmed';
var sr_lang_views_cookie = 'sr_lang_views-'.concat(sr_lang_curr);
var sr_lang_choice = vjs_readCookie(sr_lang_cookie);
var sr_lang_confirmed = vjs_readCookie(sr_lang_confirmed_cookie);
var sr_lang_views = vjs_readCookie(sr_lang_views_cookie);
// set sr_lang_views cookie to a value if null.
if (sr_lang_views === null) {
    sr_lang_views = 3.5; // this corresponds to 4 views of the links
    vjs_createCookie(sr_lang_views_cookie,sr_lang_views,3650);
}
var sr_trans_el = document.getElementById('translations');
var sr_lang_choice_url;
if (sr_lang_choice) {
         if ("pt" === sr_lang_choice) {                sr_lang_choice_url = 'https://fbref.com/pt/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats';
         }
         if ("en" === sr_lang_choice) {                sr_lang_choice_url = 'https://fbref.com/en/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats';
         }
         if ("fr" === sr_lang_choice) {                sr_lang_choice_url = 'https://fbref.com/fr/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats';
         }
         if ("it" === sr_lang_choice) {                sr_lang_choice_url = 'https://fbref.com/it/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats';
         }
         if ("de" === sr_lang_choice) {                sr_lang_choice_url = 'https://fbref.com/de/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats';
         }
         if ("es" === sr_lang_choice) {                sr_lang_choice_url = 'https://fbref.com/es/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats';
         }
}

var sr_trans_closer_el = document.querySelector('#translations .closer');
var sr_trans_welcome_el = document.querySelector('#translations .welcome');
var sr_trans_use_el = document.querySelector('#translations .use');
var sr_trans_langs_el = document.querySelector('#translations .langs');

/* *********************************************************************
   # Usage       :   sr_check_translation();
   # Purpose     :   the kickoff script for the translation paths users can follow
   # Returns     :   nothing
   # Parameters  :   none
   # Throws      :
   # See Also    :
   # Comments    :   called by default in the page, and then we call again later
                     if that did not work.
   ********************************************************************** */
function sr_check_translation() {

   // do not run if we are on the live server.
   if (!sr_trans_el || sr_lang_views < 0) {
      console.log('Modernizr.is_live or no sr_trans_el or sr_lang_views < 0 is true, so skipping.');
      return false;
   }

   // this is called multiple times, so we do the following to keep us from running it 2x.
   if (Modernizr.translation_run) {
      console.log('Modernizr.translation_run is already true, so skipping sr_check_translation');
      return false;
   }
   else {
      console.log('Modernizr.translation_run is false, so running sr_check_translation');
      Modernizr.translation_run = true;
   }

   // no cookies? just return false and they have to use the nav options.
   if (!Modernizr.cookies) {
       return false;
   }
 
   // our current language does not equal the language choice and we always forward
   if (sr_lang_choice && (sr_lang_choice !== sr_lang_curr)  && (sr_lang_confirmed === 'always_forward')) {
         window.location.href = sr_lang_choice_url;
         return true;
   }
   // our current language does not equal the language choice, or no choice has been made
   else if (! sr_lang_choice && sr_lang_confirmed === 'always_forward') {
         // this should be impossible, so remove the cookies.
	 vjs_createCookie(sr_lang_confirmed_cookie,"",-1);
	 vjs_createCookie(sr_lang_cookie,"",-1);
         return true;
   }
   // user told us not to ask them in the future.
   else if (sr_lang_confirmed === 'never_question') {
         return 'false';
   }
   else if (sr_lang_curr !== sr_lang_choice) {
         // lang is chosen and confirmed, so we auto-forward them. 
         if ("pt" === sr_lang_choice) {                sr_lang_choice_url = 'https://fbref.com/pt/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats';
         }
         if ("en" === sr_lang_choice) {                sr_lang_choice_url = 'https://fbref.com/en/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats';
         }
         if ("fr" === sr_lang_choice) {                sr_lang_choice_url = 'https://fbref.com/fr/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats';
         }
         if ("it" === sr_lang_choice) {                sr_lang_choice_url = 'https://fbref.com/it/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats';
         }
         if ("de" === sr_lang_choice) {                sr_lang_choice_url = 'https://fbref.com/de/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats';
         }
         if ("es" === sr_lang_choice) {                sr_lang_choice_url = 'https://fbref.com/es/comps/8/misc/Champions-League-Stats';
         }
         if (sr_lang_choice && sr_lang_confirmed === 'always_forward') {
              window.location.href = sr_lang_choice_url;
              return true;
         }

         // if a choice has been made then we remove the welcome.
         if (sr_lang_choice) {
             if (sr_trans_welcome_el)  sr_trans_welcome_el.parentNode.removeChild(sr_trans_welcome_el);   

             if ("pt" === sr_lang_choice) {
                sr_trans_use_el.innerHTML = "Vá para esta página em português?";
                var langs_el = ''.concat('&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="sr_confirm_trans_choice(',
		                         "'pt', ","'yes', ", "sr_lang_confirmed || false",
                	                 ')">', 'SIM', '</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; ');
                langs_el = langs_el.concat('ou ');
                langs_el = langs_el.concat('&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="sr_confirm_trans_choice(',
		                         "'pt', ","'no', ", "sr_lang_confirmed || false",
                	                 ')">', 'NÃO', '</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; ');
                sr_trans_langs_el.innerHTML = langs_el;
             }

             if ("en" === sr_lang_choice) {
                sr_trans_use_el.innerHTML = "Go to this page in English?";
                var langs_el = ''.concat('&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="sr_confirm_trans_choice(',
		                         "'en', ","'yes', ", "sr_lang_confirmed || false",
                	                 ')">', 'YES', '</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; ');
                langs_el = langs_el.concat('or ');
                langs_el = langs_el.concat('&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="sr_confirm_trans_choice(',
		                         "'en', ","'no', ", "sr_lang_confirmed || false",
                	                 ')">', 'NO', '</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; ');
                sr_trans_langs_el.innerHTML = langs_el;
             }

             if ("fr" === sr_lang_choice) {
                sr_trans_use_el.innerHTML = "Aller à cette page en anglais?";
                var langs_el = ''.concat('&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="sr_confirm_trans_choice(',
		                         "'fr', ","'yes', ", "sr_lang_confirmed || false",
                	                 ')">', 'OUI', '</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; ');
                langs_el = langs_el.concat('ou ');
                langs_el = langs_el.concat('&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="sr_confirm_trans_choice(',
		                         "'fr', ","'no', ", "sr_lang_confirmed || false",
                	                 ')">', 'NON', '</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; ');
                sr_trans_langs_el.innerHTML = langs_el;
             }

             if ("it" === sr_lang_choice) {
                sr_trans_use_el.innerHTML = "Vai a questa pagina in italiano?";
                var langs_el = ''.concat('&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="sr_confirm_trans_choice(',
		                         "'it', ","'yes', ", "sr_lang_confirmed || false",
                	                 ')">', 'SÌ', '</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; ');
                langs_el = langs_el.concat('o ');
                langs_el = langs_el.concat('&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="sr_confirm_trans_choice(',
		                         "'it', ","'no', ", "sr_lang_confirmed || false",
                	                 ')">', 'NO', '</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; ');
                sr_trans_langs_el.innerHTML = langs_el;
             }

             if ("de" === sr_lang_choice) {
                sr_trans_use_el.innerHTML = "Gehe zu dieser Seite auf Deutsch?";
                var langs_el = ''.concat('&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="sr_confirm_trans_choice(',
		                         "'de', ","'yes', ", "sr_lang_confirmed || false",
                	                 ')">', 'JA', '</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; ');
                langs_el = langs_el.concat('oder ');
                langs_el = langs_el.concat('&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="sr_confirm_trans_choice(',
		                         "'de', ","'no', ", "sr_lang_confirmed || false",
                	                 ')">', 'NEIN', '</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; ');
                sr_trans_langs_el.innerHTML = langs_el;
             }

             if ("es" === sr_lang_choice) {
                sr_trans_use_el.innerHTML = "¿Ir a esta página en español?";
                var langs_el = ''.concat('&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="sr_confirm_trans_choice(',
		                         "'es', ","'yes', ", "sr_lang_confirmed || false",
                	                 ')">', 'SI', '</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; ');
                langs_el = langs_el.concat('o ');
                langs_el = langs_el.concat('&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="sr_confirm_trans_choice(',
		                         "'es', ","'no', ", "sr_lang_confirmed || false",
                	                 ')">', 'NO', '</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; ');
                sr_trans_langs_el.innerHTML = langs_el;
             }

        }
        sr_trans_el.className = 'show';
        vjs_createCookie(sr_lang_views_cookie, sr_lang_views - 1, 3650);
    }
}
sr_check_translation();
</script>

<li id="header_clubs" class="hasmore"><a href="/en/squads/">Clubs</a><div><div class="sitenav_grid three">
  
    <div>
      <h4><span class="f-i f-gb-eng">eng</span> <a href="/en/comps/9/Premier-League-Stats">Premier League</a></h4>
      <table>

          <tr>

          <tr>
            <td><a href="/en/squads/a2d435b3/Leicester-City">Leicester City</a></td>

          <tr>

<script>
function sr_menus_setupMainNav_button_inline () {
    if (sr_detect_operaMini || !("classList" in document.createElement("_"))) {
	return false;
    }
    var nav_trigger = document.getElementById('nav_trigger');
    if(!nav_trigger || !Modernizr.is_modern || nav_trigger.triggered) {
	return false;
    }
    nav_trigger.triggered = true;
    var nav = document.getElementById('nav');
    var nav_trigger_a = nav_trigger.querySelector('a');
    if (nav_trigger_a) {
	nav_trigger_a.setAttribute('href','javascript:void(0)');
	nav_trigger.onclick = function (event) {
	    nav.classList.toggle('open');
	    var is_open = nav.classList.contains('open');
	    if (is_open) {
		nav_trigger.classList.add('open');
	    }
	    else {
		nav_trigger.classList.remove('open');
	    }
	    event.preventDefault();
	    try { sr_record_analytics_event('MainNavButtonClick_inline',sr_record_directory(),sr_record_page());}
	    catch(err) {}
	};
    }
    return true;
}
sr_menus_setupMainNav_button_inline();
</script><div class="search" role="search" aria-label="Site Search for players, teams and sections">

         <th aria-label="Dribbles ContestedNumber of times dribbled past plus number of tackles" data-stat="dribbles_vs" class=" center" data-tip="<strong>Dribbles Contested</strong><br>Number of times dribbled past plus number of tackles" >Att</th>
         <th aria-label="Percentage of dribblers tackledDribblers tackled divided by dribblers tackled plus times dribbled past" data-stat="dribble_tackles_pct" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="<strong>Percentage of dribblers tackled</strong><br>Dribblers tackled divided by dribblers tackled plus times dribbled past" >Tkl%</th>
         <th aria-label="Number of times dribbled past by an opposing player" data-stat="dribbled_past" class=" center" data-tip="Number of times dribbled past by an opposing player" >Past</th>

         <th aria-label="Number of times dribbled past by an opposing player" data-stat="dribbled_past" class=" center" data-tip="Number of times dribbled past by an opposing player" >Past</th>
         <th aria-label="Matches" data-stat="matches" class=" center group_start" >Matches</th>
      </tr>

      <tr class="thead" data-row="155">
         <th aria-label="RankThis is a count of the rows from top to bottom.It is recalculated following the sorting of a column." data-stat="ranker" class="tooltip ranker sort_default_asc show_partial_when_sorting center" data-tip="<strong>Rank</strong><br>This is a count of the rows from top to bottom.<br>It is recalculated following the sorting of a column.">Rk</th>

<!-- global.nonempty_tables_num: 1, table_count: 1 -->
   <div id="coverage" style="margin-bottom:60px" data-comment="style is for the inner nav frozen to top of page"></div>
<div class="callout light">
    <h4>About FBref.com</h4>
    
    
    
    <p>
    FBref.com launched (June 13, 2018) with domestic league coverage for England, France, Germany, Italy, Spain, and United States. Since then we have been steadily expanding our coverage to include domestic leagues from over 40 countries as well as domestic cup, super cup and youth leagues from top European countries. We have also added coverage for major international cups such as the <a href="/en/comps/8/UEFA-Champions-League-Stats">UEFA Champions League</a> and <a href="/en/comps/14/Copa-Libertadores-Stats">Copa Libertadores</a>.
    </p>

    
    <p>
    FBref includes what we believe is one of the most complete sources for women's soccer data on the internet. This includes the entire history of the <a href="/en/comps/106/history/Womens-World-Cup-Seasons">FIFA Women's World Cup</a> as well as recent domestic league seasons from nine countries.
    </p>

    
    
    <p>
    In collaboration with <a href="https://statsbomb.com">StatsBomb</a>, we are including advanced analytical data such as xG and xA for select competitions. For more information on the expected goals model and which competitions are covered, see our <a href="/en/expected-goals-model-explained/">xG explainer</a>.
    </p>

    

    <button class="tooltip opener" data-selector="#coverage_additional" data-type="hide_after">View Additional Information</button>

    <div id="coverage_additional" class="toggleable">
        <p>
        Note that player records are likely not complete for their careers. Players may come from or move to leagues we don't currently cover. This issue will go down over time, as we add new leagues and seasons. We will never in the future have less data than we do today. <strong>FBref is currently ad-free.</strong> The only payment we will ask for is that you <a href="/feedback/">let us know if you find an issue</a>, so we can get better and better.
        </p>

        <p>You can sign up to <a href="/en/about/email">receive an e-mail</a> when new countries and features launch.</p>

        <p>For more information, see our <a href="https://www.sports-reference.com/blog/2018/06/fbref-com-launches-today">Launch Blog Post</a>, the overall <a href="/en/comps/">leagues/competition page</a> with details on leagues and seasons we include, or our <a href="/en/about/">About Page</a>.  <a href="/feedback/">Let us know if you find an issue or have a suggestion</a>.</p>

        <p>FBref is one of seven <a href="https://www.sports-reference.com/">Sports-Reference.com</a> sites.</p>
    </div>
</div>
